room_title: Escape room "Time Warp" by Cryptic Quest Escape Room Adventures in Fayetteville
room_description:
The brilliant Professor Harrington Rothchild was showing off his new steam-powered Time Machine to his top PhD candidates. But he got a little heavy-handed with the steam valves again. Instead of gently folding the time-space continuum into a neat and smoothly transverseable wormhole, he kinked it horribly. Now everything is being sucked into a vortex, rapidly spinning out of control, and hurling towards a temporal event horizon.
With only about 60 minutes before everything â€“ future, past, present - is sucked into oblivion, you and your crew must act fast. Are you ready for a steampunk adventure?
